# 3. What is Salesforce DX?

Salesforce DX (Developer Experience) is a modern development approach for Salesforce applications.

It helps developers use source-driven development and improve team collaboration.

## Features of Salesforce DX

- Scratch Orgs
- CLI (Command Line Interface)
- Source Control Integration
- Continuous Integration
- Faster Development Workflow
- Package-based Development

## Benefits

- Better teamwork
- Easier deployments
- Faster testing
- Improved version control
- Modern DevOps workflow

Salesforce DX is commonly used with GitHub and VS Code.

