# 5. Important Test Cases

## Account Test Cases
- Verify Account creation
- Verify required field validation
- Verify duplicate prevention

## Contact Test Cases
- Verify Contact is linked to Account
- Verify email validation
- Verify phone number format

## Opportunity Test Cases
- Verify Opportunity stage updates
- Verify amount calculations
- Verify Close Date validation

## Trigger Test Cases
- Verify trigger runs on insert
- Verify trigger updates related records
- Verify trigger prevents invalid data

## Flow Test Cases
- Verify Flow launches correctly
- Verify field updates happen automatically
- Verify email alerts are sent

## Batch Apex Test Cases
- Verify batch processes all records
- Verify batch handles failures correctly
- Verify governor limits are respected

